Class UpdateSchemaItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.JRecord.schema.UpdateSchemaItems
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISchemaInformation

    public class UpdateSchemaItems
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISchemaInformation
    Update a Cobol-Copybook items for use in Generating / Reading Cobol Data files. It is currently used to convert Cobol Data files to/from Xml.
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
